Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:04.94,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,«I am Hanako.»\N(с англ.: «Я — Ханако»)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.75,0:00:07.09,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,«You are my friend.»\N(с англ.: «Ты — мой друг»)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:09.20,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,«He is a teacher.»\N(с англ.: «Он — учитель»)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:11.46,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,«You are my friend.»\N(с англ.: «Ты — мой друг»)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.83,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Эй, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.14,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Чем там занят?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.99,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,А-А что такое, Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.34,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Да так…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:33.24,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Ничем.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:13.48,Episode Title,Title1,0,0,0,,Ластик
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:11.97,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,«Ластик»
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.82,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}А пружинит-то отлично!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.52,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Теперь, всё что осталось,\N засунуть её в эту коробку-с-сюрпризом!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.21,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ты у меня дождёшься, Такаги-сан.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.88,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Ч-Что такое?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:41.00,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Блин, мой пенал не открывается.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.96,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Может заклинило, когда я его уронила.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.06,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Слушай, Нисиката, не откроешь?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.52,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,А… да.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.44,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Да ладно, легко же откры—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:07.39,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Что за шум, Нисиката?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:11.76,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Эм, п-простите, пожалуйста! Ничего такого!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.85,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Не, правда, Нисиката, \Nтвоя реакция — это нечто.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.73,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,У-Умолкни, а!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:37.40,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Чёрт.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.08,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Уделала меня как щенка.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:44.21,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Самое обидное, она провернула тот же трюк, \Nкоторым я сам ей готовил.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:50.72,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,С самого начала было странно, \Nчто Такаги-сан просит помощи.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.65,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Я должен был догадаться!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.64,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Теперь нужно распланировать контр-атаку.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:00.14,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Только как же подколоть Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:10.80,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Эй…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.41,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Ч-Чего?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.28,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Можно твой ластик? Я свой забыла.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:34.90,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Забыла ластик? \NВот же бестолковая!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.93,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Возможно. Спасибо.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.50,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Я тут вспомнила…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.87,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ты в курсе, что если написать на ластике имя любимой
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.82,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,и постоянно им пользоваться,\Nтвоя любовь будет взаимной?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.41,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,А, помню, было такое.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.28,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Ты сейчас прям как малышня рассуждала.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.62,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ммм…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.53,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,«Малышня», говоришь?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.05,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ого…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.64,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Что там…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.19,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ээ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.40,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Д-Да что там…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.37,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Оо…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.16,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Там же ничего не написано, так?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:06:00.51,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Да я в жизни никогда бы как малышня себя не повёл.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:05.24,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ух ты, правда что ли?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:09.51,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Не может быть. Ты же просто снова прикалываешься.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.47,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Да? Уверен?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.76,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Серьёзно?! Разве я там что-то писал?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.24,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Да ещё и забыл?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.82,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,В-верни мне её.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.47,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Держи.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.78,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Т-Ты не так всё поняла!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:37.27,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Уверен, это кто-то ещё написал! А!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.38,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Тут же ничего нет!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.51,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Стой, Такаги-сан, у тебя же своя была!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.21,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Ауч!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.51,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Замолкни.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.97,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,П-простите меня.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:00.23,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Вогнали в краску, да ещё и отругали.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.27,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ух. Пожалуй, хватит.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.36,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Это я должен сказать!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:12.40,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Учитель, можно выйти?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.28,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Выходи.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.29,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Д-Да что же это такое?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.92,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Нужно как-то подколоть Такаги-сан.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:29.38,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Точно!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.46,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Напишу чьё-нибудь имя на её ластике
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:36.06,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}и, когда она вернётся, поржу над ней.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:39.68,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Так, так. Чьё бы имя написа—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.31,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Что? Тут уже чьё-то написано?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.10,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Н-Ничего, если я гляну?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.07,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Всего одну букву…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.83,Black Signs,Eraser,0,0,0,,По
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.30,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}«По»? По…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.95,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}А значит…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:11.58,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Это имя… не моё.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:16.95,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Не то, чтобы я сильно расстроился или типа того.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:33.66,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Чёрт!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.23,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Я должен узнать!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.04,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Всё целиком!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.00,Black Signs,Eraser,0,0,0,,Посмотри в коридор
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.03,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i0}Чё?{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.72,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,{\i1}Опять… Она меня наколола!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.90,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Нисиката, выражение твоего лица бесценно.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:14.03,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Более того, ты делал всё так, как я задумала.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.60,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Поэтому я не могу перестать подкалывать тебя!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:25.04,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Т-Ты у меня дождёшься, Такаги-сан!{Ну, заяц, погоди!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:29.50,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Однажды я подловлю тебя и верну всё сполна!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.46,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Буду ждать.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.70,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Чё, думаешь мне это не по силам?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.48,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ну, да.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.61,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Я серьёзно! Лучше держись!{Хади, бойся!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.97,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Думаю, это невозможно.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.65,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Особенно с твоим везением, когда шанс был «50 на 50».
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.18,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,А? «Шанс 50 на 50»? Ты о чём?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:49.65,Black Signs,Eraser,0,0,0,,Ни
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.44,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Не скажу.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.93,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Такая морока с этим дежурством…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:02.97,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,И почему я должен идти в школу в такую рань,\Nмыть доску и заполнять журнал?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.04,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Дежурство офигенно!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:10.38,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Как говорится: «Кто рано встаёт, тому бог подаёт».
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.99,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Стоп, это же жетон из игровых автоматов.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.06,Teacher's Assistant,Title2,0,0,0,,Дежурство
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.84,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,«Дежурство».
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.92,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Знаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:31.50,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Это отличная возможность изгадить Такаги-сан парту.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.16,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Одна мысль об этом будит во мне…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.17,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Та…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:50.20,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан уже здесь.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.18,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,И зачем?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:58.90,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Никого нет.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.90,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Подозрительно.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.32,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Мне показалось что ли?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:10.04,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Нет. Я чувствую её присутствие!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.21,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Где-то спряталась, по-любому.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.35,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Опасно.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:19.49,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Я чуть было не расслабился и не начал ликовать.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:22.71,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Где же ты? Куда спряталась?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.95,Black Signs,Shoes,0,0,0,,Такаги
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.57,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Как наивно. Это было слишком просто, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.92,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Я вижу твою торчащую из-под стола сменку.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.19,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,You're probably planning to surprise me \Nas I'm about to clean the blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:41.43,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,But I won't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.57,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Aw, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:47.48,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Day duty is such a pain. \NI'm not gonna do my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:50.58,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,No one will notice if I don't clean the blackboard, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.85,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Take that, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:57.29,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,You must be so mortified \Nthat your plan failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:02.69,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I really wanna see the look \Non Такаги-сан's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.64,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,But wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.78,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Would Такаги-сан make the simple mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.95,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,of leaving her indoor shoes \Ncompletely exposed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.62,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,No! She wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.56,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Which means that's a dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.15,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.75,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I wouldn't expect anything less from Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.22,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Well, then… Where could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:28.16,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,It's Такаги-сан. There's no way she isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:35.10,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like she's in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.32,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Then, the only place left is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.95,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I'm going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.34,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I'm gonna surprise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.68,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.74,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Sh-She's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:19.05,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.41,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.09,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Y-You were behind the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.28,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,You had no idea, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:45.26,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,This curtain is a bit see-through, \Nso I could see the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:49.51,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Damn it. She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.57,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Oh, that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:54.44,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Just remembering how you acted…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.89,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,It was worth waking up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.19,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Just for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.40,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Ага!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.04,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Чтоб тебя, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.04,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Эй, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:23.22,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Когда мы вдвоём, так тихо в классе.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.05,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Как будто весь мир для нас двоих…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:32.51,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Надеюсь, больше никто не придёт.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:38.27,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Слушай… Такаги-сан…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.77,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.13,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Неужели… Ты в меня…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.99,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Бодро-утречка!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.17,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Погодка просто класс!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:56.45,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Господи, Мина, как ты умудряешься\Nбыть такой бодрой по утрам?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:15:00.18,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Чё? Да обычная я! Обычная!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.34,Main,Sanae,0,0,0,,Утомила.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.46,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Прекрати, Санаэ-тян!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.38,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Нельзя говорить, что устала! Иначе счастье убежит!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.06,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,По телеку так сказали!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:11.85,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,И ты правда в это поверила?\NТы же знаешь, что это враньё?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.26,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Да я те говорю! {Вах! Мамой клянусь! // теперь понятно, почему такие брови}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.49,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Поэтому лучше быть бодрой!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:15.92,Main,Sanae,0,0,0,,Достала…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:17.19,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Ай-яй-яй!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.90,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Больно же, Санаэ-тян.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.23,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Перестаньте.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.81,Main Top,Mina,0,0,0,,Ну же, вы двое, попытайтесь улыбнуться!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.98,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Что-то хотел сказать, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.56,Main Top,Mina,0,0,0,,Вот так! Давайте, давайте!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.44,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Ничего особенного.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:35.26,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Кстати говоря, ты разве закончил дежурство?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.62,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Ох ты ж! Забыл!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:48.42,Funny Face,Title1,0,0,0,,Рожица
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:45.87,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,«Рожица».
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:53.74,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,How do I get one over on Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.05,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.38,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Oh, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.63,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,What are you staring at the mirror for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:02.71,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Накай-кун…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:05.82,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Were you practicing putting on \Na pretty face or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.23,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.18,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,A funny face, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.37,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Of course… Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.81,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,L-Like this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:21.34,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're kinda close \Nwith Такаги-сан, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.65,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Could it be that you like—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.46,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,He's trying to change the subject.\NIt must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.93,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Нисиката! You do like Такаги-сан, don't you—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.39,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,What's with that face, Нисиката?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:43.33,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I had no idea I had such talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.81,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,All right, let's start class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.14,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Open to page thirty-six…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.33,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:53.78,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,It just happens to be the \Nscariest teacher, Tanabe-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.98,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I'll make you laugh\Nso hard with my funny face,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:59.22,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,you'll get in deep trouble, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.63,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna make Такаги-сан laugh now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.59,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,No, be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:16.15,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I have to wait until Такаги-сан \Nstarts a conversation to mock me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.13,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,When you're about to mock someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.44,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,that's when you least expect \Nyourself to be mocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.89,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,That's when I strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:29.49,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Come at me, Такаги-сан. I'm wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.73,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Hey, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.74,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.56,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,What is it, Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.06,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.61,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,H-Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:52.70,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.24,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Shut it, Нисиката!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.34,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.29,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,S-So scary…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.77,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.83,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,I was wondering what \Nyou were trying to do, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.73,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,How unimaginative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.49,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Wha…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.61,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,You should do this with your eyebrows \Nif you want to make a funny face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.25,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,And do this with your cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.84,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:22.91,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.95,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yup, yup. Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.43,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's better than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.39,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.09,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Make your mouth look more like a duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.54,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I'm trying to make her laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:39.05,Main Top,Takagi,0,0,0,,Squeeze it tighter and glare more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.72,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,and yet, she's the one giving\N me pointers on how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.07,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,It's kinda humiliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:48.26,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,No matter! All I want is for Такаги-сан \Nto laugh and get in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.10,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.12,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.48,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,It looks way better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.53,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,So why aren't you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:00.74,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'll laugh so hard if you turn to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.66,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,All right! Take this, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.79,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Нисиката?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:23.05,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'm sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:25.76,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Jeez…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.13,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Take my class seriously, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:30.48,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.97,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,My stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:38.86,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,She's laughing really hard, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.80,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,She got me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.10,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Hey, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.15,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,If I make Tanabe-sensei angry again, I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.79,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,I gotta make sure I don't get involved \Nwith Такаги-сан during this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.78,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,You finally looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:27.46,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Let's have a staring contest. One, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:28.88,Main,Takagi,0,0,0,,Three…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.88,Main,Nishikata,0,0,0,,What's with that face, Такаги-сан?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:39.19,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Нисиката! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:43.93,Italics,Nishikata,0,0,0,,Nothing good happens\Nwhen Такаги-сан gets my heart racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:20.06,Hundred Yen,Title4,38,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}One Hundred Yen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:18.44,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,"One Hundred Yen."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:25.48,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm tired, yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:29.59,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Seriously! Don't say you're tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:31.57,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Your happiness will go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:32.79,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:46.01,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:49.30,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing. Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:50.41,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:52.38,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,I'm just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:55.06,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,What was that\Nabout your happiness going away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:55.86,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:22:58.43,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Yeah, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:22:59.64,Main,Sanae,0,0,0,,Mina,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:02.53,Main,Sanae,0,0,0,,what are you hiding under your foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:06.20,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.08,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:18.54,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,I'm the one who found that hundred yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:21.08,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,You're so greedy…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:22.54,Main,Sanae,0,0,0,,Mina…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:24.99,Main,Sanae,0,0,0,,It's a token.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:26.49,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,Aww,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:30.41,Main,Mina,0,0,0,,I said I was tired, so it turned into a token.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:33.31,Main,Yukari,0,0,0,,You're still on about that?
